Various tweaks on a range of Hyper sonic based weapony to try and better hone in on the designated targert area, as they currently they are over shooting them by either going right out of the atmosphere, or over shooting the targer by several dozen to several hundred km/s. May have to make adjustments to missile core in BDArmory and add an improved missilebase, launch, and guidance systems for the hypersonic varients of larger scaled weapons

